	(gr_text "A mod for the Ikea Pencil Light, created by @obob\n\nFeatures\n- XIAO ESP32-3C\n- Can use both LiPo AND Barrel Jack\n- Can charge LiPo when on mains (4000mAh at 0.5C)"
